---
import profilePicture from '../assets/profile.png';
import SKILLS from '../assets/skills.json';
import { Icon } from 'astro-icon/components';
const { src: profilePictureUrl } = profilePicture;
---
<section>
    <img src={profilePictureUrl} alt="Damián" />
    <div>
        <h1>Hola, soy Damián</h1>
        <p>Una persona inquieta, apasionada por el desarrollo y la infraestructura lógica basada en contenedores. Siempre estoy buscando aprender para encontrar formas de construir mejores soluciones.</p>
        <span class="logos">
            {SKILLS.map(({name, icon}) => <Icon name={icon} title={name}/>)}
        </span>
    </div>
</section>

<style>
    section {
        display: inline-flex;

        h1 {
            margin-bottom: 0;
        }

        img {
            margin: 20px 40px;
            background: linear-gradient(180deg, var(--accent) -45%, var(--bg-color) 20%, var(--border));
            width: 200px;
            aspect-ratio: 1;
            border-radius: 50%;
            object-fit: cover;
            object-position: top;
        }

        div {
            display: inline-flex;
            flex-direction: column;
        }
    }

    .logos {
        font-size: 32px;
        display: inline-flex;
        gap: 10px;
        color: var(--text-secondary);
        position: relative;

        svg:hover {
          animation: shake 0.4s ease-in-out;
        }
    }

    @keyframes shake {
      0%   { transform: translate(0); }
      15%  { transform: translate(-2px, 1px) rotate(-1deg); }
      30%  { transform: translate(2px, -1px) rotate(1deg); }
      45%  { transform: translate(-1.5px, 1px) rotate(-0.5deg); }
      60%  { transform: translate(1.5px, -1px) rotate(0.5deg); }
      75%  { transform: translate(-1px, 1px) rotate(-0.25deg); }
      100% { transform: translate(0); }
    }

    @media (width <= 1024px) {
        section {
            flex-direction: column;
            img {
                max-width: 200px;
                margin-right: auto;
                margin-left: 0;
            }
        }
    }
</style>
